  "paras": [
    {
      "n": "¶ 1",
      "text": "In the hills above the old town stood a monastery whose gates had not opened to outsiders in decades. Its <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abbot\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"मठाधीश\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Ek monastery (matth) ka sabse bada pramukh ya incharge.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab religious institution ke head ki baat ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Abbot ne naye monks ka swagat kiya monastery ke gate par.'\" data-example=\"The abbot welcomed the visiting monks into the quiet stone monastery.\">Abbot</span> was a quiet man named Brother Elias, who had governed the order since before most townspeople were born."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 2",
      "text": "Lately, something strange had happened — the usual noise of the town had begun to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abate\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"घटना / कम होना\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Kisi cheez ki tezi ya taakat dheere dheere kam ho jaana — jaise tufan, dard ya gussa.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab koi intensity, force ya feeling kam ho rahi ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Baarish thodi der mein abate ho gayi aur dhoop nikal aayi.'\" data-example=\"The storm finally began to abate after raging for three hours.\">Abate</span>. The market grew quiet, the festival was cancelled, and no one could explain why. Journalist Meera called it a genuine <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Aberration\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"विचलन / असामान्यता\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Normal ya expected raah se hat jaana — ek ajeeb ya alag ghatna.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab kuch unusual ya out-of-character ho jaaye.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Uska gussa hona ek aberration tha — woh hamesha shaant rehta hai.'\" data-example=\"His sudden outburst was an aberration — he was usually calm and composed.\">Aberration</span> and decided to find out more."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 3",
      "text": "She learned that Brother Elias performed his <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Ablution\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"स्नान / शुद्धिकरण\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Khud ko dhona, aksar dharmik ritual ke roop mein.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab religious cleansing ya bathing ritual ki baat ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Yatri subah nadi mein apni ablution karte the.'\" data-example=\"Pilgrims performed their morning ablutions in the sacred river.\">Ablution</span> at dawn each day by the river below the monastery — a ritual he had never once skipped in forty years. This time, he had missed three mornings in a row."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 4",
      "text": "The monastery's official records used a strange <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abbreviation\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"संक्षिप्त रूप\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Kisi lambe shabd ya phrase ka chhota roop, jaise UN, USA.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab kisi lambi cheez ko short form mein likhna ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'UN, United Nations ka abbreviation hai.'\" data-example=\"“UN” is a common abbreviation for the United Nations.\">Abbreviation</span> for donations — \"B.E.F.\" — that no one in town could explain. To Meera, chasing this thread felt almost <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Absurd\" data-pos=\"Adj.\" data-hindi=\"बेतुका / असंगत\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Bilkul anuchit, illogical ya hasyaaspad cheez.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab koi baat ya situation bilkul bewakoofi bhari lage.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> '3 baje raat ko meeting rakhna bilkul absurd tha.'\" data-example=\"It seemed absurd that the meeting was scheduled for 3 a.m.\">Absurd</span>, but she pressed on anyway."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 5",
      "text": "Rumours spread that the Abbot planned to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abdicate\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"पद/राजगद्दी त्यागना\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Apna adhikar, gaddi ya power formally chhod dena.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab koi king ya official apni power khud chhode.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Raja ne apni gaddi abdicate kar di beete ke haq mein.'\" data-example=\"The ageing king decided to abdicate the throne in favour of his son.\">Abdicate</span> his position. When the <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abdication\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"पदत्याग\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Gaddi ya power chhodne ki wo action/process.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab kisi ke power chhodne ki ghatna describe karni ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Uski abdication ne poore desh ko chaunka diya.'\" data-example=\"The abdication shocked the nation, as no one expected the queen to step down.\">Abdication</span> was finally announced, the whole town gathered outside the gates, stunned that their quiet leader was stepping down."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 6",
      "text": "Brother Elias explained that he wished to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abnegate\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"त्याग करना\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Khud ko jaan-boojh kar kisi cheez se vanchit rakhna, aksar comfort ya pleasure se.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab koi apni khushi ya haq khud chhode kisi bade maqsad ke liye.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Sanyasi ne saari duniyavi sukh-suvidha abnegate kar di.'\" data-example=\"The monk chose to abnegate all worldly pleasures.\">Abnegate</span> the comforts of his position and live simply. He also wanted the monastery to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abolish\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"उन्मूलन करना / समाप्त करना\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Kisi purani pratha, kanoon ya system ko poori tarah khatam kar dena.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab koi law ya system officially band ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Sarkar ne purana tax kanoon abolish kar diya.'\" data-example=\"The government moved to abolish the outdated tax law.\">Abolish</span> an old rule that barred local <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Aboriginal\" data-pos=\"Adj.\" data-hindi=\"आदिवासी संबंधी\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Kisi desh ke sabse purane, mool niwasiyon se sambandhit — colonists se pehle ke.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab kisi jagah ke original/native logon ki baat ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Museum mein Aboriginal art ki khaas exhibit thi.'\" data-example=\"The museum celebrated the rich history of Aboriginal art.\">Aboriginal</span> families from worshipping there."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 7",
      "text": "For generations, the <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Aborigines\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"आदिवासी / मूल निवासी\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Kisi desh ke original, sabse pehle rehne wale log.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab kisi region ke native logon ka zikr ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Us ilaake ke aborigines sadiyon se yahan reh rahe the.'\" data-example=\"The aborigines of the region had lived off the land for centuries.\">Aborigines</span> of the valley had been quietly turned away at the gate. Elias called it the monastery's greatest shame, one he intended to correct before he left."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 8",
      "text": "Meera wanted to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abridge\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"संक्षिप्त करना\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Kisi likhi hui cheez ko bina matlab khoye chhota kar dena.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab kisi lambi kitaab ya document ko short karna ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Editor ne bacchon ke liye novel ko abridge kar diya.'\" data-example=\"The editor had to abridge the novel for the young readers' edition.\">Abridge</span> her long investigation into something readable — a short <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abridgement\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"संक्षिप्त रूप\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Kisi badi rachna ka chhota, summarized version.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab kisi lambi kitaab ka short version padhna ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Usne poori kitaab padhne se pehle uska abridgement padha.'\" data-example=\"She read an abridgement before attempting the full original.\">Abridgement</span> the town could actually finish reading before the Sunday paper went to print."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 9",
      "text": "Her editor, however, wanted to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abrogate\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"निरस्त / रद्द करना\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Kisi kanoon, samjhaute ya agreement ko formally rad kar dena.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab koi treaty ya law officially cancel ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Nayi sarkar ne purana samjhauta abrogate kar diya.'\" data-example=\"The new administration voted to abrogate the treaty.\">Abrogate</span> the whole story, fearing backlash from the monastery's old donors. Meera refused, worried the truth might simply <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abscond\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"फरार होना\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Chupke se, achanak bhaag jaana taaki pakda na jaaye.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab koi paisa ya jimmedari chhod ke bhaag jaaye.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Accountant company ka paisa lekar abscond ho gaya.'\" data-example=\"The accountant absconded with the company's funds before the audit.\">Abscond</span> into silence forever."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 10",
      "text": "When she finally published it, the town did not react with anger but with something closer to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Absolution\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"क्षमा / पाप मुक्ति\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Kisi ke paapon ya galtiyon ki formal, dharmik maafi.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab religious forgiveness ya guilt se mukti ki baat ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Usne priest se apne paapon ki absolution maangi.'\" data-example=\"He sought absolution from the priest after years of guilt.\">Absolution</span> — as if a long-held guilt had finally been allowed to surface and heal."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 11",
      "text": "The mayor's office moved to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Accelerate\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"गति बढ़ाना\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Speed badhana, ya kisi kaam ko jaldi hone dena.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab kisi process ya vehicle ki speed badhani ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Company ne product launch ki date accelerate kar di.'\" data-example=\"The company decided to accelerate the launch date.\">Accelerate</span> the reforms Brother Elias had proposed, and within a month the monastery gave Meera a rare public <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Accolade\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"सम्मान / प्रशस्ति\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Kisi achievement ke liye diya gaya award ya tareef.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab kisi ko public recognition ya honour mile.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Scientist ko uski research ke liye accolade mila.'\" data-example=\"The young scientist received an accolade for her research.\">Accolade</span> for her reporting."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 12",
      "text": "Not everyone was pleased. A former <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Accomplice\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"अपराध में साथी\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Woh insaan jo kisi crime ya galat kaam mein saath deta hai.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab crime mein kisi ka partner ya helper ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Police ko shak tha ki woh chori mein accomplice tha.'\" data-example=\"Police believe he acted as an accomplice in the robbery.\">Accomplice</span> of the old donor group tried to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Accord\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"सामंजस्य होना\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Kisi baat ya values se mel khaana, harmony mein hona.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab do cheezein ya vichar consistent ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Uske kaam uske kahi baaton se accord nahi karte.'\" data-example=\"His actions did not accord with the values he claimed to hold.\">Accord</span> his own version of events, hoping to twist the story back in his favour."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 13",
      "text": "A retired <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Accountant\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"लेखाकार\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Woh insaan jiska pesha hisaab-kitaab aur accounts rakhna hai.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab finance ya accounts sambhalne wale professional ki baat ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Accountant ne report submit karne se pehle har invoice check ki.'\" data-example=\"The accountant reviewed every invoice before the report.\">Accountant</span> who had once managed the monastery's books came forward too, offering blunt, <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Acerbic\" data-pos=\"Adj.\" data-hindi=\"कटु / तीखा\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Bahut teekha, kadwa ya harsh swabhav ya bhasha.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab koi bahut sharp aur cutting tone mein bole.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Uske acerbic comments ne sabko chup kara diya.'\" data-example=\"The critic was known for his acerbic reviews.\">Acerbic</span> testimony about decades of quiet discrimination hidden in the ledgers."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 14",
      "text": "The town hall meeting where he spoke had famously poor <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Acoustics\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"ध्वनिविज्ञान\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Dhwani (sound) ka vaigyanik adhyayan — kaise awaaz kisi jagah mein travel karti hai.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab kisi hall ya theatre ke sound quality ki baat ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Us hall ki acoustics itni buri thi ki aadhi awaaz peeche nahi pahunchi.'\" data-example=\"The hall's acoustics were so poor that half the audience couldn't hear.\">Acoustics</span> — but everyone in the room understood every word. Most townspeople chose to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Acquiesce\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"अनिच्छा से मान लेना\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Bina protest kiye, mann se na chahte hue kisi baat ko maan lena.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab koi bina bahas kiye chup chaap agree kar le.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Kaafi bahas ke baad woh finally acquiesce ho gayi.'\" data-example=\"After hours of argument, she finally acquiesced to his demands.\">Acquiesce</span> to the new reforms without protest."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 15",
      "text": "A local court was even asked to formally <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Acquit\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"दोषमुक्त करना / बरी करना\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Court dwara kisi ko not-guilty ghoshit karke crime se azad karna.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab legal case mein kisi ko nirdosh saabit kiya jaaye.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Jury ne sirf do ghante mein accused ko acquit kar diya.'\" data-example=\"The jury took only two hours to acquit the defendant.\">Acquit</span> the Aboriginal families of old, false accusations once used to justify keeping them out. There was an <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Acrid\" data-pos=\"Adj.\" data-hindi=\"तीखा / कड़वा\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Bahut hi teekhi aur beswaad gandh ya swaad, jo irritate kare.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab koi smell ya taste bahut sharp aur unpleasant ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Plastic jalne ki acrid gandh poori workshop mein fail gayi.'\" data-example=\"An acrid smell of burning plastic filled the workshop.\">Acrid</span> taste of shame in the air, and a brief flash of <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Acrimony\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"कटुता / कड़वाहट\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Kisi jhagde ya dispute mein gehri kadwahat ya dushmani ki bhavna.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab kisi conflict mein bahut zyada bitterness ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Talaak ki proceedings mein bahut acrimony thi dono taraf se.'\" data-example=\"The proceedings were marked by unusual acrimony between both sides.\">Acrimony</span> from a few old traditionalists — but it passed."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 16",
      "text": "On the day the gates finally opened to everyone, a travelling <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Acrobat\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"नट / कलाबाज़\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Woh performer jo apni body ko control karke gymnastic feats dikhata hai.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab circus ya stunt performer ki baat ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Acrobat 30 feet uunchi wire par bina dare chal raha tha.'\" data-example=\"The acrobat balanced effortlessly on a wire thirty feet up.\">Acrobat</span> performed in the courtyard for the children of the valley — the first celebration the <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abattoir\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"बूचड़खाना\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Woh jagah jahan janwaron ko maans banane ke liye kaata jaata hai.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab meat industry ya slaughter house ki baat ho.<br>💬 <b>Example:</b> 'Gaon ke bahar ek purana abattoir tha jahan sab log darte the jaane se.'\" data-example=\"The old abattoir on the edge of town had operated for sixty years.\">Abattoir</span> town had seen in years."
    }
  ]
}